Original Text:
Turn on the battery and APU and power up the radios asap.\
\
Make sure the UHF radio is set to 260 (channel 2).\
\
Do not start the engines without first obtaining clearance from the tower.\
\
\
Translated Text:
打开电池和辅助动力装置（APU），并尽快启动无线电。  \
\
确保UHF无线电设置为260（频道2）。  \
\
在未获得塔台许可前，不要启动引擎。

Original Text:
All radio commands should be made via the F10 menu, including control of your wingman once airborne, ATC and AWACS.\
\
Failure to follow ATC proceedures will result in mission failure.\
\
Please make sure radios are tuned correctly throughout the mission.\
\
\
\
Translated Text:
所有无线电指令应通过F10菜单进行，包括在空中对僚机的控制、空中交通管制（ATC）和预警机（AWACS）。  \
\
未能遵循空中交通管制程序将导致任务失败。  \
\
请确保在整个任务中无线电设置正确。

Original Text: You acheived the mission objective but as you failed to follow the ATC procedures the overall mission is a fail.

Original Text:
Lt. Hill is tasked with leading a two ship to the island of Abu Musa and neutralising the recently deployed mobile SA-15 and a pair of currently grounded Mig-21 interceptors.\
\
*** You will be taking off as a large formation of aircraft, you will be the eighth A-10 in line for taxi. ***\
Translated Text:
希尔中尉（玩家）的任务是率领两架飞机前往阿布穆萨岛，摧毁近期部署的机动SA-15和两架仍停在地面的Mig-21截击机。\
\
*** 打击编组将作为一个大型编队起飞，你将是滑行队列中的第8架A10。 ***

Original Text:
Operation Persian Freedom commences and the air war starts as waves of coalition aircraft head for Iran to establish air superiority.\
\
As part of the opening salvo the pilots of the 74th FS receive their first assignment, the neutralisation of new threats on the islands of Sirri and Abu Musa.\
Translated Text:
“波斯自由行动”开始了。随着许多波次的联军飞机，前往伊朗并建立空中优势，空战正式打响。\
\
作为首轮打击的一部分，第74战斗机中队的第一个任务，是消除西里岛和阿布穆萨岛上的新威胁。

Original Text:
PLAYER:  Tower, Gunman 2-1 requesting startup.\
\

\
Translated Text: 迪哈夫拉塔台：Gunman 2-1，允许滑行，右转进入滑行道A，然后左转进入E，停在13左跑道前。

\

\
\

Original Text: AL DHAFRA TOWER:  Gunman 2-1, you are in violation of ATC procedures, you are ordered to land immediately.

\
\

Translated Text: NEWARK 1-1：塔台，Newark编队请求起飞许可。

Original Text: AL DHAFRA TOWER:  Newark you are cleared for takeoff runway 13L.\
Translated Text: 迪哈夫拉塔台：Newark，允许从13左跑道起飞。

\

Original Text: DAVY:  Gunman 1-1 to Gunman 2-1 comms check over.\
PLAYER:  Gunman 2-1 read you Lima Charlie.
PLAYER:  Copy.
DAVY:  Copy Gunman 2-1.  Let me know when you’re ready for taxi, we’ll be departing as a formation.
Translated Text: DAVY：明白，Gunman 2-1。准备好滑行时通知我，我们将以编队起飞。

Original Text: DAVY:  Gunman 1-1 to Gunman 2-1 comms check over.
DAVY:  Copy Gunman 2-1.  Let me know when you’re ready for taxi, we’ll be departing as a formation.
Translated Text: DAVY：明白，Gunman 2-1。准备好滑行时通知我，我们将以编队起飞。

Original Text: DAVY:  Tower Gunman flight ready for taxi.\

AL DHAFRA TOWER:  Gunman you are cleared to taxi to runway 13L, follow Alpha then left turn for Foxtrot.\
\
Translated Text: 迪哈夫拉塔台：Gunman，允许滑行至13左跑道，沿A滑行道，然后左转进入F。

Original Text:
DAVY:  Alpha then Foxtrot, Gunman 1-1.\
\
PLAYER:  Gunman 2-1 ready for taxi.\

DAVY:  Ok flight let's roll, you’re on me.  Gunman 2-1 bring up the rear, we’ll collect you on the way past.\
\
Translated Text: DAVY：好的，编队开始滑行，跟着我。Gunman 2-1跟在最后，在我们经过你时跟上来。

Original Text: DAVY:  OK listen up Gunman flight...today is the real deal and this is the first time most of you are going into harm’s way.\
Translated Text: DAVY：好的，注意听Gunman编队……今天是实战任务，这是你们大多数人第一次进入危险区域。

Original Text: DAVY:   Keep calm and keep your heads and don't make mistakes.  I want to be counting all seven of you back down in a few hours time.\
Translated Text: DAVY：保持冷静，保持清醒，不要犯错。我希望在几个小时后看到你们七个人都活着回来。

Original Text: DAVY:  Once airborne we will head direct for WP1 angels 5.  I want all countermeasures and weapons set by the time we reach WP2.
Translated Text: DAVY：起飞后，我们将直接前往航路点1，高度5,000英尺。我希望在到达航路点2时，所有对抗措施和武器都已准备就绪。

Original Text: DAVY:  This is going to be another historic day for the Flying Tigers, Desert Storm was 20 years ago and it’s about time we remind the world what the Warthog can do.  Let's get out there and get the job done! \
Translated Text: DAVY：这将是我们飞虎队（第74战斗机中队的绰号，承袭自二战援亚的美籍志愿大队）的又一个历史性时刻。沙漠风暴已经是20年前的事了，是时候让世界重新认识疣猪攻击机的能力了。出发，该我们上场了！

Original Text:
DAVY:  Tower Gunman flight requesting takeoff.\
\
AL DHAFRA TOWER:  Gunman you are cleared for immediate takeoff runway 13L.\
Translated Text: 迪哈夫拉塔台：Gunman，允许立即从13左跑道起飞。

Original Text: DAVY:  Gunman 1-1 to Gunman 2-1, what's your status?\
DAVY:  Gunman 3-1, status?\

MONO:  Gunman 3 good to go.\
\
\
DAVY:  Gunman flight push to WP2, angels 15.  Switch VHF AM to Overlord.\
Translated Text: DAVY：Gunman编队前往航路点2，高度15,000英尺。切换VHF AM到Overlord。

Original Text:
PLAYER:  Gunman 1-1, Gunman 2 all present and correct.\
\
Translated Text: 玩家：Gunman 1-1，Gunman 2全员到位，一切正常。

Original Text: DAVY:  Overlord, Gunman in play.\
DAVY:  Gunman 1-1, copy Overlord. \

OVERLORD:  Copy Gunman proceed as fragged.  Picture is clean.\
\
\
Translated Text: OVERLORD：收到Gunman，按计划执行。空域安全。

Original Text: OVERLORD:  This is Overlord, calling Nevada.
OVERLORD:  This is Overlord...Florida, say again Florida.\
OVERLORD:  All flights proceed as fragged, picture remains clean.  \
Translated Text: OVERLORD：所有编队按计划执行，空域仍安全。

Original Text:
DAVY:  Gunman flight continue on, check in at WP 4.  \
\
Translated Text: DAVY：Gunman编队继续前进，在航路点4报到。

Original Text: GUNMAN 3-1:  Copy, Gunman 3-1.\

PLAYER:  Gunman 2-1 copy.\
\
\
DAVY:  Gunman 1-1 to Gunman flights.\
DAVY:  We’re approaching WP4, I’m taking my flight down to sea level.  Proceed on your flight plans and hit the targets as fragged.  Clear your attack through Whiplash before proceeding.
Translated Text: DAVY：我们正在接近航路点4，我将带领我的编队下降到海平面。按照你的飞行计划执行任务，按计划打击目标。发动打击前，通过Whiplash获准攻击。

Original Text: DAVY:  Good luck Gunman 2, see you back at the Big D.\
Translated Text: DAVY：祝好运，Gunman 2，回到迪哈夫拉再见。

Original Text: PLAYER:  Go ahead 1-1.\
PLAYER:  2-1 Copy.\
MONO:  Standing by.\

MONO:  Copy lead.\
\
DAVY:  Whiplash, Gunman 1-1 inbound on Fenway.\
DAVY:  Gunman 1-1\

WHIPLASH:  Copy Gunman 1-1, continue on mission.\
\
\
DAVY:  Whiplash, Gunman 1-1 solid kill on Fenway, solid kill Fenway.\

DAVY:  First pass took down 4 targets but we’ve still got intact launchers down there we’re going to position for a re-attack.\
\
Translated Text: DAVY：首次攻击摧毁了4个目标，但还有发射车完好。我们打算重新定位，再次攻击。

Original Text: DAVY:  This is Gunman 1, taking heavy AAA over the target, we’re bugging out.\
Translated Text: DAVY：这里是Gunman 1，在目标区域遭遇猛烈防空炮火，我们正在撤离。

Original Text:
DAVY:  Overlord, Gunman 1-1 RTB.  \
\
OVERLORD:  Copy Gunman 1-1.\
WHIPLASH:  Copy Gunman 1-1, Fenway down.\
DAVY:  SAM launch, Gunman 1 defending.\
DAVY:  Another SAM, going evasive.\
DAVY:  SAM launch, breaking...this shit is getting heavy.\
Translated Text: DAVY：导弹发射，正在规避……该死的，越来越糟了。

Original Text:
MONO:  Gunman 3 in on Wrigley.\
\
MONO:  This is Gunman 3-1.  Wrigley came up dry, nothing here.  3-2 has developed an aircraft issue so we’re RTB.\
Translated Text: MONO：这里是Gunman 3-1。Wrigley没有发现目标，什么都没有。3-2出现了飞机故障，我们正在返航。

Original Text: WHIPLASH:  Copy Gunman 3 you are clear to proceed.\
PLAYER:  Whiplash this is Gunman 2-1 inbound on Yankee.\

WHIPLASH:  Copy Gunman 2-1, you are cleared to continue on planned strike.  We have a UAV monitoring the target and the Tor is still in it’s briefed location.  Those Migs also have support vehicles around them and looks like they’re still out of play.  \
Translated Text: WHIPLASH：收到Gunman 2-1，可以继续，按计划攻击。我们有一架无人机在监视目标，Tor仍在预定位置。那些米格战机周围还有支援车辆，看起来它们仍未投入使用。

Original Text: WHIPLASH:  However we have eyes on two truck mounted Zeus’s, one on the east of the island and a second just north of the runway centre.\
Translated Text: WHIPLASH：不过，我们发现了两辆卡车载的Zeus防空炮（ZU-23-2），一辆在岛的东侧，另一辆在跑道中心以北。

Original Text: PLAYER:  Copy Whiplash, two AAA threats east and centre of the island.\
Translated Text: 玩家：收到Whiplash，两处防空炮威胁，分别在岛的东侧和中心。

Original Text: WHIPLASH:  Contact us once your attack is completed, our JTAC we may have something more for you.\
Translated Text: WHIPLASH：攻击完成后与我们联系，我们的JTAC（前线空中管制）可能还有其他任务给你。

Original Text:
CONDOR 3:  Whiplash, this is is Condor 3.\
\
WHIPLASH:  Go ahead Condor 3.\
CONDOR 3:  That Hip is on the move again, eastern LZ heading back to sea.\
Translated Text: CONDOR 3：那架河马（Mi-8直升机）又开始移动了，正从东部降落区向海上返回。

Original Text: WHIPLASH:  Copy Condor 3, thanks for the update.\
WHIPLASH:  Gunman 2-1 did you copy Condor three’s last?\
Translated Text: WHIPLASH：Gunman 2-1，你收到Condor 3刚才的消息了吗？

Original Text:
PLAYER:  Solid copy Whiplash.  \
\
WHIPLASH:  Iranians have a cargo ship off shore, they’re ferrying supplies into the airfield as we speak.  Ignore them for now Gunman 2-1, we’ll deal with them soon enough.\
Translated Text: WHIPLASH：伊朗人在近海有一艘货船，他们正在向机场运送补给。暂时忽略他们，Gunman 2-1，我们很快会处理。

Original Text:
PLAYER:  Whiplash, Gunman 2-1.  Attack complete.\
\
WHIPLASH:  Copy Gunman 2-1.  Standby for BDA….\
WHIPLASH:  Gunman 2-1 targets destroyed, neither the Tors or Fishbeds will be a threat anymore.
Translated Text: WHIPLASH：Gunman 2-1，目标已摧毁，Tor系统和米格战机不再构成威胁。

Original Text: WHIPLASH:  Gunman 2-1, the eastern Tor is still a threat, get in there and finish the job.
Translated Text: WHIPLASH：Gunman 2-1，东部的Tor系统仍具威胁，继续完成任务。

Original Text: WHIPLASH:  Gunman 2-1, the western Tor is still a threat, get in there and finish the job.\
Translated Text: WHIPLASH：Gunman 2-1，东部的Tor系统仍具威胁，继续完成任务。

Original Text: WHIPLASH:  Gunman 2-1, you’ve not put both Migs out of action yet.\
Translated Text: WHIPLASH：Gunman 2-1，你还没有瘫痪那两架米格战机。

Original Text: WHIPLASH:  Gunman 2-1, both the SA-15s are still in action!
Translated Text: WHIPLASH：Gunman 2-1，两部SA-15导弹系统仍在运作！

Original Text: WHIPLASH:  Gunman 2-1, we’ve been observing the Iranians are constructing an EWR site on the airfield, what do you say to putting it out of action? \
Translated Text: WHIPLASH：Gunman 2-1，我们侦察到伊朗人在机场上正在建设一个预警雷达站（EWR），能否瘫痪掉它？

Original Text: PLAYER:  Copy Whiplash, I say let's bring the pain.\
Translated Text: 玩家：收到，Whiplash，没问题，我们确实该给他们点颜色看看。

Original Text: WHIPLASH:  Ok then Gunman 2-1, standby for further instructions.  \

STRIKER 1-1:  Whiplash, Striker 1-1 has target acquired.\
\
WHIPLASH:  Striker 1-1 you are cleared to engage.\
STRIKER 1-1:  Copy Whiplash, Striker 1-1 rifle 2.\
Translated Text: STRIKER 1-1：收到，Whiplash，Striker 1-1，空地导弹两枚，发射。

Original Text:
WHIPLASH:  Gunman 2-1 before we get to that radar I need you to pull back to the south of the island angels 12.\
\
Translated Text: WHIPLASH：Gunman 2-1，在我们攻击那个雷达之前，我需要你撤回到岛屿南部，高度12,000英尺。

Original Text: WHIPLASH:  You’re going to see some fireworks to the NE of the island, the navy is taking care of that ship.\
Translated Text: WHIPLASH：你会看到岛屿东北方向有火光，海军正在处理那艘船。

Original Text: STRIKER 1-1:  2 miles out.\
CONDOR 3:  Good hit, good hit.  She’s on fire, I think she’s done for.\
Translated Text: CONDOR 3：命中，确认命中。它着火了，我觉得它完蛋了。

Original Text: WHIPLASH:  Good work Striker 1-1 you may depart.\
STRIKER 1-1:  Copy, Striker 1-1 RTB.\
CONDOR 3:  Woah, we’ve got big secondaries on that ship...she must’ve been packed full of ammo.\
Translated Text: CONDOR 3：哇，那艘船发生了剧烈的二次爆炸……它一定装满了弹药。

Original Text: WHIPLASH:  Gunman 2-1 lets deal with that radar and then get you out of there.  I'm gonna pass you off to Condor 3, they will talk you onto the target.  \
Translated Text: WHIPLASH：Gunman 2-1，解决那个雷达，然后离场。我会把你交给Condor 3，他们会引导你攻击目标。

Original Text: WHIPLASH:  Condor is on VHF FM 30.7, make contact and engage the target.  Whiplash out.\
Translated Text: WHIPLASH：Condor在VHF FM 30.7频率上，联系他们并攻击目标。Whiplash完毕。

Original Text: PLAYER:  Gunman 2-1 to Condor 3, we’re ready to engage that radar site.\
Translated Text: 玩家：Gunman 2-1呼叫Condor 3，我们准备攻击那个雷达站。

Original Text: CONDOR 3:  Copy Gunman 2-1, the target is a Russian built P19 radar.  It’s at the end of a dirt track and the only dish on the island.  Do you need a talk on to locate?\
Translated Text: CONDOR 3：收到，Gunman 2-1，目标是俄制P19雷达。它位于一条土路的尽头，是岛上唯一的雷达天线。你需要口述引导吗？

Original Text:
PLAYER:  Negative Condor, I have tally.\
\
Translated Text: 玩家：不用了，Condor，我已目视目标。

Original Text: PLAYER:  Affirmative Condor, I’ve yet to acquire visual.\
Translated Text: 玩家：需要，Condor，我还没找到它。

Original Text: CONDOR 3:  OK locate the east end of the runway, you should see the number 26.\
Translated Text: CONDOR 3：好的，找到跑道的东端，你应该能看到编号26。

Original Text:
PLAYER:  Ok I have it.\
\
\
PLAYER:  Tally target.\
CONDOR 3:  Now move along the runway until you see the two thick lines, your target is 500 feet north.\
Translated Text: CONDOR 3：现在沿着跑道移动，直到看到两条粗线，你的目标在北面500英尺处。

Original Text: CONDOR 3:  Ok Gunman 2-1, type 3 control is in effect.  I want you to circle the island and use the northern tip as your IP.\
Translated Text: CONDOR 3：好的，Gunman 2-1，执行三类管制。我希望你绕岛飞行，并以北端作为你的起始点。

Original Text: CONDOR 3:  Attack heading 179.  Recommend standoff attack with guns or maverick.\
Translated Text: CONDOR 3：攻击航向179。建议使用机炮或小牛导弹进行远程攻击。

Original Text:
CONDOR 3:  Those Zeus’s are located 5000 feet west and 2500 feet south east of the target so avoid overflying the target and egress on 045.\
\
Translated Text: CONDOR 3：那些Zeus防空系统位于目标西5,000英尺和东南2,500英尺处，因此避免飞越目标，脱离航向045。

Original Text: CONDOR 3:  You are cleared hot.\
PLAYER:  Condor 3, attack complete.\
PLAYER:  Copy Condor 3, switching to Whiplash.\

CONDOR 3:  Good work Gunman 2-1, your work here is done.  Handing you back to Whiplash.\
\
\
Translated Text: CONDOR 3：干得好，Gunman 2-1，你的任务完成了。我将你交回给Whiplash。

Original Text:
PLAYER:  Whiplash, Gunman 2-1 is RTB at this time.\
\
WHIPLASH:  Copy Gunman 2-1, good work.  You are cleared to depart, switch back to Overlord.\
Translated Text: WHIPLASH：收到，Gunman 2-1，干得好。允许离开，切回Overlord。

Original Text:
PLAYER:  Overlord, Gunman 2-1 egressing Yankee and heading home.\
\
OVERLORD:  Overlord copies Gunman 2-1. \
PLAYER:  Condor 3, Gunman 2-1.  We are unable to follow through on that radar we are RTB.\
Translated Text: 玩家：Condor 3，Gunman 2-1。我们无法继续攻击那个雷达，正在返航。

Original Text: CONDOR 3:  Copy Gunman 2-1.  Looks like we’ll have to drum up some more support.  Handing you back to Whiplash.\
Translated Text: CONDOR 3：收到，Gunman 2-1。看来我们需要更多支援。我将你交回给Whiplash。

Original Text: DAVY:  Gunman 1-1 to Gunman 2-1.  Report status.\
DAVY:  Outstanding work Gunman 2-1.\

DAVY:  Copy 2-1, at least you got the primary mission done, someone else will have that radar down before we know it.\
\
Translated Text: DAVY：收到，2-1，至少你完成了主要任务。其他人会解决掉那个雷达，我们很快会得知结果的。

Original Text: DAVY:  How are you for fuel Gunman 2-1.\
DAVY:  Ok 2-1, get yourself back to Al Dhafra, I’ll see you on the ground.  Gunman 1-1 out.\
Translated Text: DAVY：好的，2-1，返回迪哈夫拉，一会地面见。Gunman 1-1完毕。

Original Text: DAVY:  Ok 2-1, in that case I want you to divert to Al Minhad.  I’ll make sure they’re expecting you.\
Translated Text: DAVY：好的，2-1，那样的话，我建议你备降至艾尔明翰。我会通知他们做好接应准备。

Original Text:
PLAYER:  Gunman 2-1 is RTB at this time, all primary targets destroyed and we also bagged a new radar site before it went active.\
\
Translated Text: 玩家：Gunman 2-1，正在返航，所有主要目标已摧毁，我们还摧毁了一个尚未启用的新雷达站。

Original Text: PLAYER:  Gunman 2-1 is RTB at this time, all primary targets destroyed, we were also tasked with a new radar site by JTAC but we came up short.\
Translated Text: 玩家：Gunman 2-1，正在返航，所有主要目标已摧毁，JTAC（联合终端攻击管制员）还指派了一个新的攻击雷达站任务，但我们未能完成。

Original Text: PLAYER:  Fuel is good, I’ve plenty for the journey back.\
Translated Text: 玩家：燃油充足，足够返航。

Original Text: PLAYER:  Fuel is looking a little low, not sure I’ll make it back to Al Dhafra.\
Translated Text: 玩家：燃油不太够了，不确定能否返回迪哈夫拉。

Original Text: PLAYER:  Al Minhad tower this is Gunman 2-1.  I’m low on fuel and diverting from Al Dhafra.  Request permission to land.\
Translated Text: 玩家：艾尔明翰塔台，这里是Gunman 2-1。我燃油不足，从迪哈夫拉备降。请求降落许可。

Original Text: AL MINHAD TOWER:  Gunman 2-1 you are cleared for immediate landing runway 09.\
Translated Text: 艾尔明翰塔台：Gunman 2-1，允许立即降落，跑道09。

Original Text:
DARKSTAR:  Gunman 2-1, this is Darkstar.  Picture is clean at this time.\
\
\
DARKSTAR:  Gunman 2-1, Darkstar.  Picture is clean.\
OVERLORD:  Gunman 2-1, Darkstar is tracking a pair of bandits attempting to slip across the straits.\
Translated Text: OVERLORD：Gunman 2-1，Darkstar正在跟踪2架试图穿越海峡的敌机。

Original Text:
OVERLORD:   Colt is moving to intercept, they shouldn’t pose a threat to you but be prepared to react if the situation changes.  Switch to monitor Darkstar on 141.8.  \
\
Translated Text: OVERLORD：Colt正在前往拦截，他们不会对你构成威胁，但如果情况有变，做好反应准备。切换到141.8监控Darkstar。

Original Text: DARKSTAR:  Colt, Darkstar, bandit, BRA 020 for 90.  Angels 22, hot.\
Translated Text: DARKSTAR：Colt，这里是Darkstar，敌机，方位020，距离90，高度22000英尺，迎头。

Original Text: PLAYER:  Copy Overlord, switching to Darkstar\
DARKSTAR:  Colt, Darkstar, bandit, BRA 020 for 60.  Angels 22, hot.\
Translated Text: DARKSTAR：Colt，这里是Darkstar，敌机，方位020，距离60，高度22000英尺，迎头。

Original Text: DARKSTAR:  Colt, Darkstar, bandit, BRA 020 for 30.  Angels 22, hot.\
Translated Text: DARKSTAR：Colt，这里是Darkstar，敌机，方位020，距离30，高度22000英尺，迎头。

Original Text: GUNMAN 1-1:  Gunman 2-1, Darkstar is tracking a pair of bandits attempting to slip across the straits.
Translated Text: GUNMAN 1-1：Gunman 2-1，Darkstar正在跟踪2架试图穿越海峡的敌机。

Original Text: GUNMAN 1-1:   Colt is moving to intercept, they shouldn’t pose a threat to you but be prepared to react if the situation changes.  Switch to monitor Darkstar on 141.8.
Translated Text: OVERLORD：Colt正在前往拦截，他们不会对你构成威胁，但如果情况有变，做好反应准备。切换到141.8监控Darkstar。

Original Text: MONO:  So Steep did you find the target range ok on your last flight?\
Translated Text: MONO：Steep，你上次任务中找到靶场了吗？

Original Text: MONO:  You got that right, you know I used to fly the alpha model, it’s amazing the difference the avionics upgrades make to how accurate we can be…\
Translated Text: MONO：说得没错。我跟你说，我以前飞的是A型。升级了新航电后，打击精度比起曾经，简直就是两种飞机。

Original Text: MONO:  ...and we used to be pretty darn accurate in that.\
Translated Text: MONO：……虽说……我们以前其实也打的挺准的。

Original Text: MONO:  Hey boss you remember how we used to use the Mav as a FLIR before we had the Litening pod?\
Translated Text: MONO：嘿，长官，你还记得在我们有Litening吊舱以前，是怎么拿小牛导弹当红外成像（FLIR）用的吗？

Original Text: MONO:  I don’t miss that one bit, it’s amazing we used to hit anything!\
Translated Text: MONO：那段日子我一点都不怀念，我们用那玩意居然还能命中目标，真是个奇迹。

Original Text: MONO:  Well Steep I certainly think you lucked out getting a Hog squadron for your assignment, I for one like going to war in a Titanium bathtub.\
Translated Text: MONO：Steep，我觉得你被分派到我们这开疣猪是很幸运的。我个人非常享受坐在钛合金浴缸里上战场的感觉。

Original Text:
MONO:  This plane can take a lot of punishment and still limp home, when it comes to combat the Hog is the place to be.\
\
Translated Text: MONO：这架飞机在遭受巨量攻击后仍能勉强返航。要论对地作战，疣猪永远是最合适的。

Original Text: PLAYER:  Yeah, the nav systems on this aircraft are something else.   And this airplane is a hell of a weapons delivery platform as well.\
Translated Text: 玩家：找到了。这架飞机的导航确实挺独特的。而且这飞机还是个极好的武器投放平台。

Original Text:
DAVY:  Christ mono I really do.\
\
\
\
\
\
Translated Text: DAVY：草（一种植物），Mono，别提了，我可记的太清楚了。

Original Text: PLAYER:  Lead can we review the threats we’re facing again?\
Translated Text: 玩家：领队，能再给我们讲讲要应对的威胁吗？

Original Text: PLAYER:  2-1 copy.\
MONO:  Davy I still think you’re crazy going head on with an SA-6 without proper SEAD.\
Translated Text: MONO：Davy，我还是觉得你在没有适当SEAD（防空压制）的情况下，就正面冲SA-6阵地，太疯狂了。

Original Text:
MONO:  Sitting duck though if you get it wrong…\
\
\
\
\
Translated Text: MONO：如果出了差错，你就是活靶子……

Original Text: DAVY:  Copy 2-1, Fenway is protected by an SA-6 SAM system.  My flight will deal with this, Gunman 2 and 3 you will bypass it on the way to your targets.\
Translated Text: DAVY：收到，2-1，第一个目标Fenway由SA-6防空导弹系统保护。我的编队会处理这个，Gunman 2和3，你们在前往目标的路上绕过它。

Original Text: DAVY:  That’s why we’re going in low, we’ll handle it.\
Translated Text: DAVY：我知道，所以我们会低空进场。没事，我们会解决掉它的。

Original Text: DAVY:  2-1 your target is protected by an SA-15, this is a very dangerous system if you get close to it, but the good news is that it’s very limited in range.\
Translated Text: DAVY：2-1，你的目标由SA-15保护。如果靠得太近，它相当危险，但好在它射程很短。

Original Text: DAVY:  The max engagement range of the Gauntlet is about the same as that of a Maverick so I would advise a standoff attack.\
Translated Text: DAVY：SA-15的最大交战距离和小牛导弹差不多，我建议你远程攻击。

Original Text: DAVY:  The limited missile range also means a lower engagement ceiling, we believe it’s somewhere in the angels 20-25 range, you might be able to go high and drop a GBU on it as well.\
Translated Text: DAVY：有限的射程，同时也意味着较低的射高，我觉得差不多在20000到25000英尺之间。所以你也可以尝试高空投放GBU。

Original Text: DAVY:  I would also expect MANPADs in the area as well, remember these are limited to very short range and a max ceiling of around angels 12...so stay high if you overfly the island.\
Translated Text: DAVY：此外，我觉得那个区域会有MANPADs（便携式防空导弹）。它们射程非常短，射高约12,000英尺……所以如果飞越岛屿，保持高空。

Original Text:
DAVY:  If you must get lower then keep dumping flares, I recommend you set a CMS programme to do this for you.\
\
Translated Text: DAVY：如果你必须降低高度，那就不停投热诱，我建议你设一个CMS（对抗系统）程序专门干这个。

Original Text: PLAYER:  I’ve always loved that plane, when I was a kid I saw one at the air tattoo at RAF Waddington, 2001 I think...loved it ever since.\
Translated Text: 玩家：我一直很喜欢那架飞机。小时候我在…，嗯…，应该是2001年沃丁顿的皇家国际航展上，见过一架……从那时起就一直很喜欢。

Original Text: MONO:  Man those B1’s are really something when they take off.\
MONO:  You know we actually use it as a CAS platform.
Translated Text: MONO：实话讲，我们其实是把它当成CAS（近距离空中支援）平台用的。

Original Text:
DAVY:  Probably scare the crap out of any enemy troops on the ground if it came over low.\
\
\
Translated Text: DAVY：这东西低空飞过，会把地面上的敌军吓坏的。

Original Text: MONO:  Never be a match for the Hog though!\
Translated Text: MONO：不过还是永远比不上咱们的疣猪！

Original Text: MONO:  Can’t get into tight areas like we can but it does the job.\
Translated Text: MONO：它不能像我们一样进入狭小区域，但它也能很好的完成它的任务。

Original Text: PLAYER:  That's odd, the SA-15 doesn't appear to be active.
